        {
            "title": "消委會｜新任總幹事仍在招聘中 署理總幹事何應富：會適時公布新人選",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"何應富表示新任總幹事的招聘程序正進行中，會適時公布新人選。何君健攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/47299cf12b3fe2f737c9de29abe2f20f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051514341516204.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">何應富表示新任總幹事的招聘程序正進行中，會適時公布新人選。何君健攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>消委會今日（15日）發表新一期《選擇》月刊，由署理總幹事何應富主持，他表示新任總幹事的招聘程序正進行中，會適時公布新人選，在新的總幹事上任前，會由他擔任署理總幹事一職。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249845/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃鳳嫺已於本月6日約滿離任。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9cbf185228697aacf90f67996832e293/2025-05/NK250415CC013.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃鳳嫺已於本月6日約滿離任。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249846/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消委會今日發布新一期《選擇》月刊。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4a03c44dc3831b5b341e10fe0529e301/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250515_112951781_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消委會今日發布新一期《選擇》月刊。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249847/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"暫由何應富(右)任署理總幹事。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1c82f5b3a16dd4ffc8bb1d0008fd89d5/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250515_112951781_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        暫由何應富(右)任署理總幹事。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249848/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消委會今日發表新一期《選擇》月刊。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aa9480f26ac369ee3e25e108e4a8526b/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250515_112951781_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消委會今日發表新一期《選擇》月刊。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249849/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"新一期《選擇》月刊發布會由何應富主持。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/09162ae853f8e2ed67d16d151864d59c/2025-05/q_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        新一期《選擇》月刊發布會由何應富主持。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>何應富表示，招聘沒有遇到困難，只是有必要的程序落實確認，有許多步驟才能完成。他又指，第一次主持記者會對他而言是個新挑戰，但有團隊的協助，相信能應對傳媒的提問。\n\n</p>\n<p>消委會前任總幹事黃鳳嫺於本月6日約滿離任，消委會早前表示，已展開新任總幹事的招聘工作，並會適時公布遴選結果。\n\n</p>\n<p>記者：郭穎彤<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069056/即時-港聞-消委會-新任總幹事仍在招聘中-署理總幹事何應富-會適時公布新人選",
